Three Stanford Lake Learners have accumulated the required points for selection to the Limpopo team to participate at the South African National Level 3 Regional Championships that will take place from 3 to 6 April at Hillcrest Swimming Pool in Pretoria. They are Luca Wasley (Grade 9), Isabella Drewett and Devon Coad (both Grade 8). Only five swimmers per age group are included in the provincial team.